Package pkg1

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PlayList
    This class is meant as the playlist program It defines a PlayList which stores SongRecord objects in an array of size 50 (maximum value) Its data fields are playlistArray, name, and playlistItems It implements Cloneable because it implements Cloneable
    PlaylistOperations
    The PlaylistOperations class is the driver class for this project This class is what provides user interaction for creating the playlist
    SongRecord
    The SongRecord class is used to create song objects It contains the data fields: title, artist, minutes, seconds The method implements Cloneable because the class implements a clone method for SongRecord objects
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FullPlayListException
    This class is meant to define the custom exception FullPlayListException This exception is thrown whenever the playlist has reached its full size and another element is going to be added to it.
